Glance OVF/OVA Tool

The tool takes an OVA tar archive and extracts it, parses the OVF for
properties and uploads the disk image to Glance with the included
properties. Finally, it creates a Heat template with the cpu, memory
info from the OVF as a flavor.

Usage
$ ./ovf-tool.py <OVA-filename> [<uploaded-image-name>]
